{"id":"022543dbe3b58a1681fca19925453b701d7a289d04c90ad0f56ea226c7858d89","item_id":"40bcc39360:1","text":"PxrDisplace"}
{"id":"2d934bdd710163c22548f62919d44d169cea069c35528de195757fc75f86fa1c","item_id":"40bcc39360:2","text":"了解如何添加 scalar displacement（标量置换）、vector displacement（矢量置换）以及 displacement layers（置换层）。"}
{"id":"289a179d4a4343e55994f03beab92a0abf8234756dfc0580c3c77a4922a59a61","item_id":"40bcc39360:3","text":"将 PxrDisplace VOP 添加到 RIS Network，并连接到 PxrMaterialBuilder 的 output_collect 节点。连接你的 displacement map（置换贴图），例如创建一个"}
{"id":"6e48623fa90d586c291685ad4b209b48df9fc49e0f40d2294220229b735d62f1","item_id":"40bcc39360:5","text":"VOP 或"}
{"id":"955f4d475bb6a22d836253b921bf273ed12f22a6996aa53991fa9f067eeadbe4","item_id":"40bcc39360:6","text":"PxrPtexture"}
{"id":"44f498c28a45e0a1e03b646ee0ab9169a0c1db00d515f143271c16665e47df0a","item_id":"40bcc39360:7","text":"VOP，分别用于 texture（纹理）或 ptex。也可以连接 shading network（着色网络）。我们推荐使用基于 vector（矢量）的 displacement，尤其是在分层时。"}
{"id":"ec20923866696ec487ea86071082fc35d2aa09923e591a3c47babde3186b7a16","item_id":"40bcc39360:8","text":"将 PxrDisplace VOP 连接到 output_collect 节点的 shader 输入。"}
{"id":"cdfd49fb5b1ef6df1407c57c7785497cfc9fca2aea0390dd94eebd4d187fdafc","item_id":"40bcc39360:9","text":"Displacement 设置位于被置换 geometry OBJ 上的 RenderMan tab > Primvars > Shading > Displacement。"}
{"id":"73031a329517eca8111a753bde8a33cb644a660e7ee6c261d042c2ac06b0b6b8","item_id":"40bcc39360:10","text":"Trace displacements 默认开启。"}
{"id":"be1d59e475e69c6a249751d16e163e97754062ef4b21030729e45bd91b7bfa02","item_id":"40bcc39360:11","text":"设置 displacement bound（置换边界）以渲染置换；设为 0 会关闭对象上的 displacement（置换）。"}
{"id": "6863067eb0a2c7499425c6c189b2c88bac55ca754285a6ab1ef37b75b4cfad4d", "item_id": "40bcc39360:0", "text": "参见"}
{"id": "ccc6ebd6189c8d8f6fed82ba1bfef6ebca467a2b94a4677ddb9068b32719f8d7", "item_id": "40bcc39360:4", "text": "PxrTexture"}
